        "timestamp": "2020-12-18 16:03:26.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nSome background for the change - I wanted to make it more clear that the bpgen is supposed to be used as library, so I separated logic for commandline reading to separate module. Also that way it will be easier to use in runtime-api (no issues that the bpgen has a class annotated with @SpringBootApplication etc)\n\nLast patchset (3) I reworked the BlueprintJarComparatorTest in order to:\n - make it a little easier to maintain\n - make files cleanup happen before and after test run\n - make it more system independent (change of \"\\\\\" as path separator to File.separator)\n - remove SpringContext startup from the test (not needed)\n\nI also compared the jar from this code to jar built from the origin/master, the tests passed.",
        "patchset_number": 3
      },
